Returns the given String encoded within CDATA format to be safe for use in XML, if and only if it contains characters problematic when used in XML data.
@param valToEncode the string to encode.
@return the given string encoded as CDATA if it contains characters not allowed in XML data, or the given string unchanged if it contains no such characters.

